                           <desc>: Donation note.</desc>
                           <quote xml:lang="gez">
                              <locus target="#132rc">132rc</locus>: ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘሹም፡ አጋሜ፡ ካሳ፡ ዘወሀቦ፡
